BT 1 0 0 1 0 63 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Transfer efficiency INCREASES monotonically with gamma even as coherence COLLAPSES. This is) Tj T* /F2 9 Tf (Environment-Assisted Quantum Transport \(ENAQT\)) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( -- first identified by Mohseni et al. \(2008\) for photosynthetic energy) Tj T* (transfer. The counterintuitive result: noise HELPS transport, up to a limit. This paper derives the Goldilocks optimum where) Tj T* (the marginal benefit of additional noise \(transport gain\) equals the marginal cost \(coherence loss\), identifies the optimum as) Tj T* (gamma_Goldilocks = gamma_c / \(alpha x t\), and explains why photosynthesis evolved at 95-100% transfer efficiency) Tj T* (despite -- because of -- quantum noise.) Tj T* ET
